# Implantik by Dr. Chirap — Cursor Rules

## Stack
- Next.js 15 App Router, TypeScript strict, Tailwind + shadcn/ui
- Server Components by default; client only when needed (forms, consent, tracking)
- i18n: RO (default) + EN via `[locale]` routes

## Brand
- Primary purple: `#534AB7` — single source in `globals.css` (`--brand-purple`)
- Accent coral: `#F0997B` — sparingly
- Fonts: Poppins (display), Inter (body) via `next/font`
- Premium, airy, rounded corners, mobile-first

## CMSR / Medical advertising (mandatory)
- No result guarantees, superlatives, or comparative/denigrating claims
- No promotional offers/discounts; transparent pricing allowed
- No product brand promotion; factual service mentions only
- Stats and before/after: placeholders only, marked for client confirmation
- Civil, friendly, factual tone

## Placeholders
Never invent clinic data. Use marked placeholders: `[TELEFON CLINICĂ]`, `[POZĂ REALĂ DE ADĂUGAT]`, etc.

## Code style
- Use shadcn components; avoid custom CSS unless in globals.css tokens
- Minimize client JS; prefer Server Actions for forms
- All tracking gated behind consent (Consent Mode v2)
